    "body": "@rjmholt Thanks! Do you think that it should be part of a powershell release ?\r\nI will test it and let you guys know if it works.\r\n\r\nI will try with this `Dockerfile`: \r\n\r\n```Dockerfile\r\nFROM mcr.microsoft.com/powershell\r\n\r\nSHELL [\"/opt/microsoft/powershell/7/pwsh\", \"-C\"]\r\n\r\nRUN apt update -y;apt install nginx -y\r\n\r\n# Or with this alias 'exec'\r\nCMD  Invoke-Exec -Executable nginx -Arguments '-g','daemon off;'\r\n```\r\n\r\nAcutally it does look nice 🙈🤗\r\n",
